{
  "chapter": 4,
  "chapter_summary": "伊风自终南山出发，昼夜兼程赶往无量山寻宝。在叙州城外客栈遭遇天争教黑衣汉子挑衅，伊风隐忍未发。天媚教弟子稚凤麦慧以色诱之术接近伊风，用迷魂粉将其迷倒。伊风被带至天媚教巢穴，面对万妙仙娘和四名轻纱少女的围困。他以内功抵御迷药，假称是天争教弟子，利用\"三天教\"之间的关系成功脱身。此后伊风赶赴无量山，在深山瀑布后的山坳中发现灯火，暗示藏宝之地已有人占据，留下悬念。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_dian_xiao_er",
      "speaker_name": "店小二",
      "listener": "char_yi_feng",
      "text": "你老运气好，只剩下几间房了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣汉子",
      "listener": "char_yi_feng",
      "text": "朋友！你是哪里来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "伊风",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_da_han",
      "text": "从北边来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣汉子",
      "listener": "char_yi_feng",
      "text": "朋友，你走运啦！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣汉子",
      "listener": "char_yi_feng",
      "text": "从今天起，你就是我的兄弟了，大块吃肉，大碗喝酒。我看你买卖也不见得得意，跟着我们弟兄在一起，保管有你的好处。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 71
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "伊风",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_da_han",
      "text": "老哥的盛情，小弟心领了，但是……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_yi_da_han",
      "speaker_name": "黑衣汉子",
      "listener": "char_yi_feng",
      "text": "小子不要不识抬举，老子看上了你，你怎么样？老子……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "伊风",
      "listener": "char_hei_yi_da_han",
      "text": "住口！快给我滚开！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dian_xiao_er",
      "speaker_name": "店小二",
      "listener": "char_yi_feng",
      "text": "你老真是大人大量，不跟那般人一样见识，这才叫不吃眼前亏的大丈夫！你老看，连韩信以前都从人家的裤裆下钻过去哩！",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_hui",
      "speaker_name": "翠装少女",
      "listener": "char_yi_feng",
      "text": "我听我们那几个不成材的奴才说，有个高人，用力劲震了他的手。我就说：这小店里怎么来了个高人呀？赶紧走过来看看。哪知道……",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_hui",
      "speaker_name": "翠装少女",
      "listener": "char_yi_feng",
      "text": "我说您哪！高姓大名呀？就凭您那么俊的内功，一定是武林中成名露脸的大英雄！",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "伊风",
      "listener": "char_mai_hui",
      "text": "小可略通两手粗把式，哪里是什么高人，更谈不上成名露脸了。方才是一时失手，伤了贵——贵管家，还望姑娘恕罪！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_hui",
      "speaker_name": "翠装少女",
      "listener": "char_yi_feng",
      "text": "您不肯说，我也没办法。那蠢才受了伤，是他有眼不识泰山，活该倒霉！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_hui",
      "speaker_name": "翠装少女",
      "listener": "char_yi_feng",
      "text": "你肯不肯和我做个朋友？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "伊风",
      "listener": "char_mai_hui",
      "text": "承姑娘抬爱，小可实感有幸。但小可此刻尚有要事在身，稍息片刻，使得离去，日后如有机缘，再……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_hui",
      "speaker_name": "翠装少女",
      "listener": "char_yi_feng",
      "text": "那你是不是肯交我这个朋友？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_hui",
      "speaker_name": "翠装少女",
      "listener": "char_yi_feng",
      "text": "您既然有急事，我可也不能多打扰您，可是下次见面的时候，您可不能再不理我了！",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_hui",
      "speaker_name": "麦慧",
      "listener": "char_yi_feng",
      "text": "这——这是我的名字。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "矮少女",
      "listener": "char_mai_hui",
      "text": "行了！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_nv_zi",
      "speaker_name": "矮少女",
      "listener": "char_mai_hui",
      "text": "三妹！四妹！你们去招呼教主来吧！这小子也不见得济事，还害得我们四个亲自出马。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_hui",
      "speaker_name": "麦慧",
      "listener": "char_a_nv_zi",
      "text": "他将于七双腕震伤的手法，确实高明得很！我以为他一定蛮有功夫哩！哪知道——",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_hui",
      "speaker_name": "麦慧",
      "listener": "char_a_nv_zi",
      "text": "也不中用！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_hui",
      "speaker_name": "麦慧",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "教主来了！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_miao_xian_niang",
      "speaker_name": "天媚教主",
      "listener": "char_yi_feng",
      "text": "哎哟！想不到这种地方，还有这么漂亮的角色！慧儿！你真乖！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_miao_xian_niang",
      "speaker_name": "万妙仙娘",
      "listener": "char_yi_feng",
      "text": "小孩子功夫不错嘛。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "伊风",
      "listener": "char_wan_miao_xian_niang",
      "text": "小可是奉了天争教之命，有事入滇。不知之中，冒犯了贵教，还望阁下，高抬贵手，放过小可，日后敝教教主，必有补报。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_miao_xian_niang",
      "speaker_name": "万妙仙娘",
      "listener": "char_yi_feng",
      "text": "小孩子！不要怕，张开眼睛好了，本教主又不会吃了你。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_miao_xian_niang",
      "speaker_name": "万妙仙娘",
      "listener": "char_yi_feng",
      "text": "本教主早就猜到你是天争教下的徒弟，'三天'之外，若还有像你这样的年轻好手，那么，我们那位老头子又要气死了。喂，我说……",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_miao_xian_niang",
      "speaker_name": "万妙仙娘",
      "listener": "char_yi_feng",
      "text": "小兄弟，也是我跟你投缘，还舍不得放你走，我看你要是不急的话，还是在这里多呆几天吧。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "伊风",
      "listener": "char_wan_miao_xian_niang",
      "text": "教主宠召，小可何幸如之！只是小可实在有急事，一刻也耽误不得。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_feng",
      "speaker_name": "伊风",
      "listener": "char_wan_miao_xian_niang",
      "text": "只是小可滇中之事一完，必然尽快赶来向教主问安的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wan_miao_xian_niang",
      "speaker_name": "万妙仙娘",
      "listener": "char_yi_feng",
      "text": "你要是真有急事，你就快去。可是回来的时候，可不要忘了再来看我呀！不然，下次再让我撞着，不把你这小鬼撕成两半才怪！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mai_hui",
      "speaker_name": "麦慧",
      "listener": "char_yi_feng",
      "text": "恭喜你呀！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    }
  ],
